   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">If the cursor hovers over a piece of equipment on a screen and a “lightning bolt” appears,
         click on the item to open a faceplate (popup window] that provides information about that
         specific device. The faceplates vary depending on the type of equipment. For example, the
         faceplates for a screw drive or dosing feeder are shown below, and include the ability to
         change operating modes, change parameter values, and view alarms for that particular
         device.</p>
